        div.container
            h2 .grid-col-
                span X
            p The grid is a a fluid grid with a max width, that shrinks with the browser/device at smaller sizes. The max width can be changed with one line of CSS and all columns will resize accordingly. The syntax is simple and it makes coding responsive much easier. Go ahead, resize the browser.

